title: Megatokyo[1-1084][ENG][gif]
description:
Megatokyo is an English-language webcomic created by Fred Gallagher and Rodney Caston.
Set in a fictional version of Tokyo, Megatokyo portrays the adventures of Piro, a young fan of anime and manga, and his friend Largo, a video game enthusiast.
